Shrey:
def computer_to_phone(numbers):
    comp=['7','8','9','4','5','6','1','2','3','0']
    phon=['1','2','3','4','5','6','7','8','9','0']
    ans=''
    for i in numbers:
        a=comp.index(i)
        b=phon[a]
        ans=ans+b
    return ans

Question: https://www.codewars.com/kata/57cc79ec484cf991c900018d
Shruti:
def db_sort(arr): 
    l=[]
    s=[]
    r=[]
    print(arr)
    for i in arr:
        if type(i)==int:
            print(i)
            l.append(i)
            print(l)
        else: 
            print(i)
            s.append(i)
            print(s)
    l.sort()
    s.sort()
    for j in l:
        r.append(j)
    for k in s:
        r.append(k)
    print(r)
    return r
